    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html><html style=\"font-size: 85px;\"><head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1\">\n    <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n    <meta name=\"renderer\" content=\"webkit\">\n    <title>清华大学建筑学院</title>\n    <meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"清华大学建筑学院,建筑学院,世界一流,建筑学,中国特色，城市规划，建筑系\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"清华大学是中国著名高等学府，是中国高层次人才培养和科学技术研究的重要基地。清华大学的前身是清华学堂，成立于1911年。截至2017年，清华大学设有20个学院、58个系，已成为一所具有理学、工学、文学、艺术学、历史学、哲学、经济学、管理学、法学、教育学和医学等学科门类的综合性、研究型、开放式大学。截至2017年8月31号，清华大学在学学生总数为47762人，其中本科生15619人、硕士生19062人、博士生13081人。\">\n   \n    <link href=\"/sites/css/font.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/index.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link href=\"/sites/css/phone.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.min.css\">\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/jquery-3.3.1.min.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/js.js\"></script>\n    <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/sites/js/swiper/swiper-3.4.2.jquery.min.js\"></script>\n</head>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<body>\n<div class=\"headD\"></div>\n   \n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"head\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n        <a href=\"\" class=\"logo\"></a>\n        <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"navA\"></a>\n        <dl class=\"btn\">\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/INDEX\" class=\"on\">CN</a></dd>\n            <dd><a href=\"/column/Home\">EN</a></dd>\n            \n            \n \n            \n            \n            <dd class=\"search\" value=\"搜索\"> \n              <form name=\"form1\" id=\"search-form-header\" action=\"/column/search\" target=\"_blank\" method=\"post\">\n                   <div class=\"input\">    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"curpage\" value=\"1\">\n\t               <input name=\"key\" type=\"text\" class=\"inp\" value=\"\" onfocus=\"this.value=''\" onblur=\"if(this.value==''){this.value='';}\">\n                </div>  \n\t         </form>\n        \n           </dd>  \n            <div class=\"submit\">      \n                 <a id=\"searchbtn\" href=\"javascript:;\" onclick=\"$('#search-form-header').submit();\" class=\"btn\" title=\"搜索\">搜索</a>\n           </div> \n      \n            \n        </dl>\n        <div class=\"nav\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jj\">简介</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/dt\">动态</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/xs\">系所</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/zs\">招生</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jx\">教学</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/ky\">科研</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/rw\">人物</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/jl\">交流</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"/column/lj\">链接</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"characterShow_01\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n         <div class=\"info\"><a href=\"/column/INDEX\">首页</a><a href=\"/column/rw\"><b>·</b>人物</a>  <a href=\"/column/sz\"><b>·</b>师资</a>  <a href=\"/column/rw_jzhj\"><b>·</b>建筑技术科学系</a>  </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"name\">张昕</div>\n        <div class=\"msg\">\n            电话：86-10-62782206 <br>\n            传真：86-10-62770314 <br>\n            E-mail：zhx@tsinghua.edu.cn\n        </div>\n    \n       <div class=\"img\"><img src=\"/upload_files/image/1681868400163_C2.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n   \n    </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"wal characterShow\">\n   \n     <div class=\"content\"><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研究和教学方向：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">教育经历：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span>1996-2001</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">清华大学建筑学学士</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span>2001-2005</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">清华大学建筑技术科学博士</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">专业履历：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">清华大学建筑学院</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">剑桥大学访问学者（</span><span>2012-2013</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">课程教学：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）执教《一年级建筑设计》，年均</span><span>24</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">周教学（</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下、</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">上、</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">下）。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）参加《三年级开放式教学》，</span><span>2023</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">年以建院未来畅想</span><span>2035</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">——</span><span>AI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">生成式影像为题。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）执教《设计专题》，以“日常情境中的光学人因研究与设计”为题。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）负责《建筑光环境》，以研究型课程论文为载体，植入研究方法与论文写作教学。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）负责《建筑物理环境》，承担</span><span>16</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学时建筑光学教学。。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）负责《建筑类论文写作方法》，承担</span><span>10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学时教学。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）作为《建成环境研究方法论》的主讲教师，负责课程组织、管理、考核。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持本科教学改革项目《守正创新——立足设计科学的建筑类交叉探索类人才培养体系构建》。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">研究项目：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以提升建成环境中人的绩效、舒适、健康为目标，融合建筑学与照明学，重新架构建筑光学的理论体系，聚焦学科交叉对于两个学科的知识贡献，并拓展至神经建筑学、人因工程、智能座舱、睡眠医学、光电子学等领域。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">以天然光为基准的照明人因研究：既有照明标准均出自严格的人工光实验，隔绝天然光与视野，不符合真实建成环境的特点。为回答真实情境中的人因问题，主持多项长时自然实验和实况实验，获取天然光的地域、时域与节律特征，创新成果可优化人的位置和朝向、天然光与人工光的配置、透光材料与视野图像等，也为地下、水下等极限环境中人工光模拟自然情境奠定了数字基础。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）参加清华大学丰田联合研究基金专项：建成空间界面人因化设计与产品；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持清华大学自主科研计划关键核心技术专项：狭小封闭（</span><span>ICE</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）空间的节律照明研究——朝向与时间暗示的重建；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持</span><span><a href=\"https://webvpn.tsinghua.edu.cn/http/77726476706e69737468656265737421fbee5984203c7044301c9aa596522b20dfc68f3fca7b1af1/business/vprojectAction!to_view.action?entity.id=26ef84cd79d52d8e0179f4f89fad2e6f&amp;isPersonalCenter=false&amp;ck=D4G54WU7C3XLOGIWZXRO8C9W75DUUC8B&amp;ck=D4G54WU7C3XLOGIWZXRO8C9W75DUUC8B\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"项目查看\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: windowtext\">中冶置业集团儿童房健康照明研究</span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持清华大学丰田联合研究基金专项：车内动态节律光环境对驾驶员与乘客的生理及心理影响研究；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持国家自然科学基金面上项目：模拟天然光节律照明的漫透射假窗系统于日间应用的关键问题研究；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持</span><span><a href=\"https://webvpn.tsinghua.edu.cn/http/77726476706e69737468656265737421fbee5984203c7044301c9aa596522b20dfc68f3fca7b1af1/business/vprojectAction!to_view.action?entity.id=16560842&amp;isPersonalCenter=false&amp;ck=D4G54WU7C3XLOGIWZXRO8C9W75DUUC8B&amp;ck=D4G54WU7C3XLOGIWZXRO8C9W75DUUC8B\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"项目查看\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: windowtext\"><span>清华大学建<span>筑学院</span></span></span><span style=\"color: windowtext\">-</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;color: windowtext\"><span>西<span>顿联合照<span>明实验室设计与<span>研究</span></span></span></span></span></a></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>7</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持阳光城集团“绿色智慧家”照明标准体系研究；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>8</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）参加国家重点研发计划：交通建筑室内热环境、光环境研究及气流分布特性及其对空调能耗的影响机理；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持国家自然科学基金面上项目：天然光非视觉生物效应对中青年睡眠质量与觉醒度的关联影响研究；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持国家自然科学基金面上项目：中国零售照明模型与节能策略研究；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>11</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持国家自然科学基金面上项目：中国传统建筑光环境保护；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>12</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）主持北京市自然科学基金：太阳光导入器提供北京地下空间照明的建筑光学关键技术；</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">）担任国家</span><span>863</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">计划子课题负责人：国家体育馆和奥运村照明系统规划设计、集成结构分析、系统评价和标准。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">获奖荣誉：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">长期从事建筑光环境的设计研究，提出以光为驱动的建筑师与照明设计师的协作设计方法，三次参展威尼斯双年展中国国家馆。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">主持完成了中国传统建筑光环境保护的理论建构与保护技术流程，并应用于现代建筑实践。主持完成了故宫代表建筑倦勤斋、符望阁、慈宁宫的光环境溯源设计，实现了北京传统四合院的纸窗天然光环境溯源；建立了窗纸性能测度、模拟方法，发明“纸玻璃”应用于故宫重要展陈实践，推动纸窗技术发展。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">主持完成了包括</span><span>31</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">个单体的松阳乡建照明实践，用光诠释</span><span> “</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">建筑针灸</span><span>”</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">理论，提出以</span><span>“</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">暗</span><span>”</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">为出发点的乡建照明设计方法，“松阳故事”参加威尼斯双年展主展等系列大展，获得国际学术界广泛关注，成为我国美丽乡村建设的经典案例与示范工程。松阳石门廊桥、红糖工坊等获得</span><span>9</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">项国际照明奖。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 28px; line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\";font-family: 宋体\">主持完成了首钢单板滑雪大跳台、冬奥组委办公区与首钢三高炉的照明设计，以及延庆赛区照明总体设计、张家口赛区夜景照明统筹等重要冬奥项目，为国家</span><span style=\";font-family:华文细黑\">重大活动探索出了低碳可持续性的夜景新形态</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">。上述工作被制作为中央广播电视总台大型微纪录片《一起上冰雪》第一集，于</span><span>CCTV10/</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">奥林匹克频道等媒体发布（全网累计播放</span><span>2.8</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">亿次）。</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">期</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">刊文章：</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>1</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">）张昕</span><span>*, </span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">唐博</span><sup><span>&amp;,</span></sup> <span style=\";font-family:宋体\">陈晓东</span><sup><span>&amp;</span></sup><span style=\";font-family: 宋体\">，董英俊</span><sup><span>&amp;</span></sup><span>. </span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">建筑光学中人因研究的进展与方法</span><span>. </span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">科学通报</span><span>, 2022, 67(16): 1771</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">–</span><span>1782</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">（</span><span>2</span><span style=\";font-family:宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">Yingjun Dong<sup>&amp;</sup>, <strong>Xin&nbsp;Zhang</strong>*. Study on the&nbsp; effect&nbsp; of&nbsp; awakening daylight&nbsp; in&nbsp; dormitories&nbsp; on&nbsp; morning alertness, mood, fatigue and sleep quality&nbsp; of&nbsp; college students, Building and Environment, Jun </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px\">2021, 203</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 1px\">：</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px\">0-108060</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 1px\">（</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 1px\">）</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">张昕</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">*</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">，周昕怡<sup><span>&amp;</span></sup>，陈晓东<sup><span>&amp;</span></sup></span><span>. </span><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">从“教室采光”到“课桌采光”——基于不良利用时间占比的中小学教室采光标准重评估<span>.</span>世界建筑，<span>2021</span>（<span>3</span>）：<span>36-41</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">（<span>4</span>）</span><span>Xiufang Zhao</span><sup><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">&amp;</span></sup><span>, </span><strong><span>Xin Zhang</span></strong><span>*</span><span>, Kai Cui. Recreating the Tibetan Traditional Lighting in Local Modern Library: Research-Based Lighting Design in Yushu Library</span><span>. Light and Engineering, Nov 2019, 27(3): 47-54</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span><span>5</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）</span><strong><span>Xin Zhang*</span></strong><span>. Lighting - Led Architecture: A Collaborative Approach. Architectural Design, Dec 2018, 88(6): 102-109</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">（</span><span>6</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">Tong&nbsp;Liu<sup>&amp;</sup>, <strong>Xin&nbsp;Zhang</strong>*. Dynamic simulation on eye exposure of in-vehicle daylighting in urban environments of China, Transportation Research Interdisciplinary Perspectives, Dec 2022(16):100727</span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">（<span>7</span>）崔思瑶<sup><span>&amp;</span></sup>，<strong>张昕</strong><span>*. </span>位置如何影响大学生自习行为的认知和评价——一项基于神经建筑学视角的自然实验<span>.</span>世界建筑，<span>2022</span>（<span>11</span>），<span>114-115</span></span></p><p style=\"line-height: 27px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 华文细黑\">（<span>8</span>）<span>Xinyi&nbsp;Hao<sup>&amp;</sup>, <str